it</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>The straightforward algorithm for calculating a floating-point dot produ=
ct of vectors can suffer from <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cata=
strophic_cancellation" title=3D"Catastrophic cancellation">catastrophic can=
cellation</a>. To avoid this, approaches such as the <a href=3D"https://en.=
wikipedia.org/wiki/Kahan_summation_algorithm" title=3D"Kahan summation algo=
rithm">Kahan summation algorithm</a> are used.
</p>
